<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM6.3">
<l>intira ṉuḷḷiṭṭa tēvarku ḻāmellām</l>
<l>vantirun teṉṉaima kaṭpēci mantirittu</l>
<l>mantirak kōṭi yuṭutti maṇamālai</l>
<l>yantari cūṭṭak kaṉākkaṇṭēṉ tōḻīnāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O friend! I dreamt that Durgā adorned [me] with the wedding garland,</l>
<l>dressing [me] up with the wedding clothes</l>
<l>after the whole group of gods including Indra</l>
<l>came and, staying [here], settled me as the bride</l>
<l rend="indent">consulting [with each other].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
